Director Of Technical Solutions
Director Of Technical Solutions
Location:  --Dubai
Salary:  GBP0 - GBP601000 per annumRegional Director for Technical Solutions and Business Development:
1.       Translate customer energy solution requirements and needs into best-in-class solutions  for the customer
2.       contract management support
3.       Working with the technical team for putting together the bid in terms of pricing, quantity, contract terms, payment terms.
4.       Bid management à interface with Sales Management (together with Regional Director Sales), Product Management, Implementation, Service and Operations , R&D, corporate functions and client, to manage and lead the bid.
5.       Drive the company’s products portfolio according to future market requirements
6.       Develop the business into new markets
7.        Focal point between Dubai office and HQ for technical bid management
8.       operational control of dedicated running projects
9.       Liaise with HQ R&D and Product Management to further develop existing products and solutions
10.   Introduce new solutions and products to meet specific customer needs
11.   Find, manage and support the selection of business partners for common solutions in the region
12.   Support the Managing Director of the Middle East region in the business development activities
13.   Support the Managing Director in the development of solution positioning and pricing strategies for the region;
14.   Supporting the MD in setting strategies and yearly budgets for the region
